#: ../../docs/server_manual/services/wcs.rst:2
msgid "Web Coverage Service (WCS)"
msgstr "Web Coverage Service (WCS)"

#: ../../docs/server_manual/services/wcs.rst:4
msgid ""
"The **1.0.0** and **1.1.1** WCS standards implemented in QGIS Server provide"
" a HTTP interface to access raster data, referred to as *coverage*, coming "
"from a QGIS project."
msgstr ""
"WCS standardi **1.0.0** i **1.1.1** implementirani u QGIS Serveru pružaju "
"HTTP interfejs za pristup rasterskim podacima, koji se nazivaju *coverage*, "
"iz QGIS projekta."

