msgid "The XML document for a 3 bands GeoTIFF raster layer looks like:"
msgstr "XML dokument za GeoTIFF rasterski sloj sa 3 kanala izgleda ovako:"

#: ../../docs/server_manual/services/wcs.rst:166
msgid "COVERAGE"
msgstr "COVERAGE"

#: ../../docs/server_manual/services/wcs.rst:168
msgid ""
"This parameter, defined in WCS ``1.0.0``, allows to specify the layers to "
"query for additional information. Names have to be separated by a comma."
msgstr ""
"Ovaj parametar, definisan u WCS ``1.0.0``, omogućava zadavanje slojeva nad "
"kojima se vrši upit za dodatne informacije. Nazivi moraju biti razdvojeni "
"zarezom."

#: ../../docs/server_manual/services/wcs.rst:171
msgid ""
"In addition, QGIS Server introduced an option to select layers by its short "
"name. The short name of a layer may be configured through "
":menuselection:`Properties --> Metadata` in layer menu. If the short name is"
" defined, then it's used by default instead of the layer's name:"
msgstr ""
"Pored toga, QGIS Server je uveo opciju za izbor slojeva po kratkom nazivu. "
"Kratak naziv sloja može se podesiti kroz :menuselection:`Svojstva --> "
"Metapodaci` u meniju sloja. Ako je kratak naziv definisan, podrazumevano se "
"koristi umesto naziva sloja:"

#: ../../docs/server_manual/services/wcs.rst:186
msgid "``COVERAGE`` is mandatory if ``IDENTIFIER`` is not set."
msgstr "``COVERAGE`` je obavezan ako ``IDENTIFIER`` nije postavljen."

#: ../../docs/server_manual/services/wcs.rst:192
msgid "IDENTIFIER"
msgstr "IDENTIFIER"

#: ../../docs/server_manual/services/wcs.rst:194
msgid ""
"This parameter replaces the :ref:`COVERAGE <wcs_describecoverage_coverage>` "
"parameter in WCS ``1.1.1``. But QGIS Server does not filter according to the"
" ``VERSION`` parameter so ``IDENTIFIER`` and ``COVERAGE`` have the same "
"effect."
msgstr ""
"Ovaj parametar zamenjuje parametar :ref:`COVERAGE "
"<wcs_describecoverage_coverage>` u WCS ``1.1.1``. Ali QGIS Server ne "
"filtrira prema parametru ``VERSION``, pa ``IDENTIFIER`` i ``COVERAGE`` imaju"
" isti efekat."

#: ../../docs/server_manual/services/wcs.rst:200
msgid ""
"``IDENTIFIER`` is mandatory if ``COVERAGE`` is not set. If both "
"``IDENTIFIER`` and ``COVERAGE`` parameters are defined, ``COVERAGE`` is "
"always used in priority."
msgstr ""
"``IDENTIFIER`` je obavezan ako ``COVERAGE`` nije postavljen. Ako su "
"definisana oba parametra, ``IDENTIFIER`` i ``COVERAGE``, uvek se prioritetno"
" koristi ``COVERAGE``."

#: ../../docs/server_manual/services/wcs.rst:208
msgid "GetCoverage"
msgstr "GetCoverage"

#: ../../docs/server_manual/services/wcs.rst:210
msgid ""
"This request allows to retrieve the coverage according to specific "
"constraints like the extent or the CRS. Standard parameters for the "
"**DescribeCoverage** request according to the OGC WCS 1.1.1 specifications:"
msgstr ""
"Ovaj zahtev omogućava preuzimanje coverage-a prema određenim ograničenjima, "
"kao što su obuhvat ili CRS. Standardni parametri za zahtev "
"**DescribeCoverage** prema OGC WCS 1.1.1 specifikacijama:"

#: ../../docs/server_manual/services/wcs.rst:1
msgid "Name of the request (**GetCoverage**)"
msgstr "Naziv zahteva (**GetCoverage**)"

#: ../../docs/server_manual/services/wcs.rst:1
msgid ":ref:`WIDTH <wcs_getcoverage_width>`"
msgstr ":ref:`WIDTH <wcs_getcoverage_width>`"

#: ../../docs/server_manual/services/wcs.rst:1
msgid "Width of the response in pixels"
msgstr "Širina odgovora u pikselima"

#: ../../docs/server_manual/services/wcs.rst:1
msgid ":ref:`HEIGHT <wcs_getcoverage_height>`"
msgstr ":ref:`HEIGHT <wcs_getcoverage_height>`"

#: ../../docs/server_manual/services/wcs.rst:1
msgid "Height of the response in pixels"
msgstr "Visina odgovora u pikselima"

#: ../../docs/server_manual/services/wcs.rst:1
msgid ":ref:`BBOX <wcs_getcoverage_bbox>`"
msgstr ":ref:`BBOX <wcs_getcoverage_bbox>`"

#: ../../docs/server_manual/services/wcs.rst:1
msgid "Map extent in CRS units"
msgstr "Obuhvat karte u jedinicama CRS-a"

#: ../../docs/server_manual/services/wcs.rst:1
msgid ":ref:`CRS <wcs_getcoverage_crs>`"
msgstr ":ref:`CRS <wcs_getcoverage_crs>`"

#: ../../docs/server_manual/services/wcs.rst:1
msgid "Coordinate reference system of the extent"
msgstr "Koordinatni referentni sistem obuhvata"

#: ../../docs/server_manual/services/wcs.rst:1
msgid ":ref:`RESPONSE_CRS <wcs_getcoverage_responsecrs>`"
msgstr ":ref:`RESPONSE_CRS <wcs_getcoverage_responsecrs>`"

#: ../../docs/server_manual/services/wcs.rst:1
msgid "Coordinate reference system of the response"
msgstr "Koordinatni referentni sistem odgovora"

#: ../../docs/server_manual/services/wcs.rst:242
msgid "BBOX"
msgstr "BBOX"

#: ../../docs/server_manual/services/wcs.rst:244
msgid ""
"This parameter allows to specify the map extent in the units of the current "
"CRS. Coordinates have to be separated by a comma. The ``BBOX`` parameter is "
"formed like ``minx,miny,maxx,maxy``."
msgstr ""
"Ovaj parametar omogućava zadavanje obuhvata karte u jedinicama tekućeg "
"CRS-a. Koordinate moraju biti razdvojene zarezom. Parametar ``BBOX`` se "
"formira kao ``minx,miny,maxx,maxy``."

#: ../../docs/server_manual/services/wcs.rst:263
msgid "CRS"
msgstr "CRS"

#: ../../docs/server_manual/services/wcs.rst:265
msgid ""
"This parameter allows to indicate the  Spatial Reference System of the "
"``BBOX`` parameter and has to be formed like ``EPSG:XXXX``."
msgstr ""
"Ovaj parametar omogućava naznačavanje prostornog referentnog sistema "
"parametra ``BBOX`` i mora biti formiran kao ``EPSG:XXXX``."

#: ../../docs/server_manual/services/wcs.rst:272
msgid "RESPONSE_CRS"
msgstr "RESPONSE_CRS"

#: ../../docs/server_manual/services/wcs.rst:274
msgid ""
"This parameter allows to indicate the output response Spatial Reference "
"System and has to be formed like ``EPSG:XXXX``. The CRS of the corresponding"
" coverage layer is used by default."
msgstr ""
"Ovaj parametar omogućava naznačavanje prostornog referentnog sistema "
"izlaznog odgovora i mora biti formiran kao ``EPSG:XXXX``. Podrazumevano se "
"koristi CRS odgovarajućeg coverage sloja."

#: ../../docs/server_manual/services/wcs.rst:282
msgid "WIDTH"
msgstr "WIDTH"

#: ../../docs/server_manual/services/wcs.rst:284
msgid ""
"This parameter allows to specify the width in pixels of the output image. "
"The resolution of the response image depends on this value."
msgstr ""
"Ovaj parametar omogućava zadavanje širine izlazne slike u pikselima. "
"Rezolucija slike odgovora zavisi od ove vrednosti."

#: ../../docs/server_manual/services/wcs.rst:291
msgid "HEIGHT"
msgstr "HEIGHT"

#: ../../docs/server_manual/services/wcs.rst:293
msgid ""
"This parameter allows to specify the height in pixels of the output image. "
"The resolution of the response image depends on this value."
msgstr ""
"Ovaj parametar omogućava zadavanje visine izlazne slike u pikselima. "
"Rezolucija slike odgovora zavisi od ove vrednosti."

#: ../../docs/server_manual/services/wcs.rst:300
msgid ""
"From left to right: ``WIDTH=20&HEIGHT=20``, ``WIDTH=50&HEIGHT=50``, "
"``WIDTH=100&HEIGHT=100``"
msgstr ""
"Sleva nadesno: ``WIDTH=20&HEIGHT=20``, ``WIDTH=50&HEIGHT=50``, "
"``WIDTH=100&HEIGHT=100``"
